tionally, we show the performance of our algorithm\nthrough an extrinsic evaluation -- we employ two tasks, like prediction and\ninformation diffusion, and show that the effect of our algorithm on these tasks\nis higher than the other baselines.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 12 Jun 2019 16:25:51 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 3 Feb 2021 17:39:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-02-04"}
