 is the prerequisite for any further\ndeterministic development of efficient, high-quality, large-scale hBN growth\nwith MOVPE.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 12 Jun 2019 18:16:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-06-14"}
