 $N$. Given a complex connection\n$\\nabla$ on $E_G$, we give a necessary and sufficient condition for $\\nabla$ to\nbe induced by a connection on $E_N$. This criterion relates Hermitian--Einstein\nconnections on $E_G$ and $E'_C$ in a very precise manner.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 12 Jun 2019 20:04:34 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-06-14"}
