s abundance or metallicity. Our results are\nconsistent with, and place in context, published numerical studies of streaming\ninstabilities.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 12 Jun 2019 20:41:21 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 26 Feb 2020 20:26:58 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 15 Apr 2020 21:13:57 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Mon, 25 May 2020 02:58:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-05-26"}
