same time, most of\nthe previous work in parameterized streaming complexity was restricted to the\nEA (edge arrival) or DEA (dynamic edge arrival) models. In this work, we\nconsider the above mentioned graph deletion problems in the four most\nwell-studied streaming models, i.e., the EA, DEA, VA (vertex arrival) and AL\n(adjacency list) models.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 13 Jun 2019 02:24:36 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 2 Oct 2019 13:30:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-10-03"}
