ground Ohmic and/or ambipolar\ndiffusivity, but drives no flux transport when it is the only non-ideal effect\npresent.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 13 Jun 2019 09:51:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-06-19"}
